## Gate checklist

The PR gate (CI) blocks merge until these hold:

- [ ] `{{command_prefix}}rigorous critique` run on the diff; block-level findings fixed
- [ ] e2e test covers the delivered functionality, with **no mocks** (real services via test containers) — required when app code changes
- [ ] docs canon up to date (`pnpm docs:check` passes)

